summary: This is a brief email from May 12, 2021, requesting the creation of a testifying witness folder for an unnamed individual and the inclusion of attached documents. It appears to be internal case preparation correspondence related to the Ghislaine Maxwell trial.
keyFacts: The document is an email dated May 12, 2021, concerning case preparation for the Ghislaine Maxwell trial.
The email requests the creation of a testifying witness folder for an unnamed individual.
The email mentions attached documents to be included in the witness's folders.
The recipient and sender are not identified by name in the provided text.
